snippet.title: POP! Culture Corner
snippet.description:
Come Join us for all the biggest castings, rumors, speculation, and reviews the Industry has to offer,
Here at POP! Culture Corner we will be taking a new approach to Podcasting/YouTube with Interactive Segments, Fun Discussions, And Guest Interviews With Actors/Directors/Crew & Many More People who make the industry possible. It doesn't matter if you just want to listen to the audio, or join us with video, the Message will always be the same, having fun, talking about the things we love and gaining some traction as we do it. Were passionate, but Consistent, and We Tell it how it is, not as we want it to be. We do it for you, we do it for the culture!!
